headline: Kimberly-Clark Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: The board of directors of Kimberly-Clark Corporation (NASDAQ: KMB) has declared a regular quarterly dividend of $1.26 per share. The dividend is payable in cash on January 5, 2026, to stockholders of record at the close of business on December 5, 2025.
